    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>領域・荒らす
許さない・
領域・荒らす……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The one...violates...this land...
Unforgivable...the one...violates...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ゴメンなさい……
エトがお邪魔しちゃって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm deeply sorry... Please, forgive
Eto for her intrusion...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>許す・おまえ・許す</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Forgive...you... Forgive...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>外・闇・
漏れた・動揺</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Darkness...leaking...outside... Disturbance...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>外が闇に包まれたのは、
シャドウの動揺が原因だって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The outside being in darkness is the
cause for Shadow feeling disturbed.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284044</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスの時も確か、
同じ原因でアーリィが
闇に包まれていました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Back during Dhaos's War, such disturbance
was present too. The entire Arlee continent
was covered in darkness like now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我・去る</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I...leave...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……はぁ……
最後まで何考えてっか
わかんなかったな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>*sigh*... It's just one thing after the other.
This doesn't make any sense...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284500</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はレ……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto, it's you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;！　&lt;Mel&gt;！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;! &lt;Mel&gt;! You're here!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりとも大丈夫だった？
けがはない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you both ok? Are you hurt?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284808</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こっちのが
心配したっての</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>WE were the ones worried here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、ぼく、ずっと
ふたりのこと
探してたかラ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...I've been looking and looking
and couldn't find you...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それでここに
迷い込んだの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And you ended up here?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>申し訳ありません。
私どもの手違いで、おふたりを
連れ去ってしまったばかりに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My deepest apologies. It is because of
a misunderstanding on my clan's part
that you three were separated...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、え……あ、はい、
キョーシュクです……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah...uhm... Much obliged...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285456</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さて、ヴォルトもいるし、
これで元の時代にも戻れるぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right! With Volt and Eto, now
we can return to your time!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレさ……
&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃん手伝うよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I want to help &lt;Suzu&gt;
with her fight.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、わたしも！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes! I want to help too!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_049&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だって、今の状態って
他人事じゃないでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With the current situation, the
problem isn't hers alone anymore.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_050&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ……&lt;Mel&gt;も
同じこと考えてたのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;'s agreeing with me?
I think hell just got colder.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_051&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この世界が、
まんまオレらの世界の
過去なんだもんな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...What happens to this world
will affect our own era, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_052&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>プルートっての、
ほっといたら、世界が
ろくなことんなんねーし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leaving Pluto alone will only make
things worse in the long run.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286000</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_053&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おし……ほんじゃ、
私も一緒に行くかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right then, I guess I have
no choice but to follow you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_058&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>みなさん、
ありがとうございます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Everyone, thank you very
much for your support!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_059&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、これは我々で
決着をつけなくては
ならないことです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>However, I cannot assure
victory just yet.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_060&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>一旦、&lt;Red&gt;忍者の里&lt;White&gt;に
戻りましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's return to &lt;Red&gt;Ninja Village&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_210_070_061&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今日のところは、
私の屋敷でゆっくりと
お休みください</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We can use my residence
to get a good rest before
the final fight.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
